refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
abstract public voidDs\Sequence::insert intindex mixedvalues
Inserts values into the sequence at a given index.

&reftitle.examples;
Ds\Sequence::insert example
<?php $sequence = new \Ds\Vector();
$sequence->insert(0, "e"); // [e] $sequence->insert(1, "f"); // [e, f] $sequence->insert(2, "g"); // [e, f, g] $sequence->insert(0, "a", "b"); // [a, b, e, f, g] $sequence->insert(2, ...["c", "d"]); // [a, b, c, d, e, f, g]
var_dump($sequence); ?>
&example.outputs.similar;
object(Ds\Vector)#1 (7) { [0]=> string(1) "a" [1]=> string(1) "b" [2]=> string(1) "c" [3]=> string(1) "d" [4]=> string(1) "e" [5]=> string(1) "f" [6]=> string(1) "g" }
